QuestData.Title: Terrors in the Deep
QuestData.Description: Azshara knows we are here. Still, we must press on.$b$bBe careful, though. There is a... wrongness coming from the water. It is unlike the magic of old, but more ancient and terrible.$b$bTraverse the canals and find the source of corruption. If we are to search Zin-Azshari, we cannot let any relics fall into the hands of even darker powers.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: This seems to be the source of the maddening whispers coming from Zin-Azshari.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat $1oa corrupted creatures and the source of the corruption.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Find Thalyssra near the Highborne Estates.
